data.description: Assumable VA loan with very low interest rate available for qualified buyers. Wonderful 4 bedroom 2 bath home in excellent location. Open concept, split bedroom floor plan great for entertaining & privacy. New in 2021 roof, hot water heater, and plumbing throughout. Electric fireplace. Updated kitchen island & new pull out drawers. Screened front porch with new tile entry, front door paint & hardware. Large master bedroom and bathroom with dual vanities & two spacious walk-in closets. Ample storage and extra closet space. Tile in wet areas, cathedral ceilings. Guest bath with exterior access and plenty of room for a pool. 10’x15’ bonus room not included in sq ft. Outdoor entertaining area, banana & pineapple plants in backyard. Minutes from water, public boat ramp, & fishing. Close to shopping center & golf course.
